patthana14.33:1.1: Pariyāpannaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1)
patthana14.33:2.1: Apariyāpannaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Apariyāpannaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca napariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. Apariyāpannaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca napariyāpanno ca naapariyāpanno ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā. (3)
patthana14.33:3.1: Pariyāpannañca apariyāpannañca dhammaṃ paṭicca naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (1) (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
patthana14.33:4.1: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… avigate pañca.
